Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.90,0:00:04.64,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The light of summer is the radiance of yesterday.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.70,0:00:06.27,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}In the aftermath of the tears lies a cheesecake.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.34,0:00:07.92,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}It's time to catch the killer,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.95,0:00:10.16,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}but we'll need Japanese, English, and German!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.26,0:00:11.70,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Recognizing that single truth,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.72,0:00:13.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}A child with the intellect of an adult...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.27,0:00:15.14,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}His name is: Detective Conan!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.39,0:01:47.49,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Our usual group went to see the Tokyo Spirits soccer game.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.32,0:02:03.32,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Unfortunately, the Spirits lost.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.16,0:02:07.12,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}We then parked to get our food.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.80,0:02:15.95,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10\an8}And then, when we returned, a German man we\Nhad met earlier named Ludger had been attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.65,0:02:15.95,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Ludger Heinen (42)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.82,0:02:21.29,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}To our surprise, Ludger{\rHonorifics - Narration Off\be10}-san{\r\be10} said "criminal" and...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:21.91,0:02:23.22,Narration Off,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Pointed at Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.83,0:02:25.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.50,0:02:26.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's me!?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.71,0:02:28.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's OK.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.38,0:02:31.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} gave us all a hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.13,0:02:33.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A hint?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.47,0:02:36.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Before he fainted, Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pointed at Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.43,0:02:40.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And said: "Criminal".
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.43,0:02:41.51,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-You?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.64,0:02:44.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.52,0:02:46.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I-It was me...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.27,0:02:51.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And then he latched onto my shoulder and muttered, "El."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:54.79,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}E—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.58,0:02:57.48,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}E—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.78,0:02:58.67,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}E—
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.30,0:03:00.66,Flashback,,0,0,0,,{\be10}El...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.12,0:03:05.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In other words, the criminal has some connection with both Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.50,0:03:09.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And whatever it is that "El" refers to.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:18.15,Title,,0,0,0,,Genta's Certain Kill Shot (Part Two)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.35,0:03:22.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You wanna know why I'm here?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.85,0:03:27.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why do I have to tell you police officers that?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.52,0:03:29.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.48,0:03:32.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inspector, here he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.77,0:03:35.48,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Excuse me, I don't have time for this...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.48,0:03:39.15,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Inagaki Hiramasa (35)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.49,0:03:43.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, bot someone was attacked here and you\Nthree are the only ones that were in the area.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.78,0:03:43.78,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Genda Tatsuzou (44)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.26,0:03:45.64,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,We ask you cooperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.49,0:03:49.76,Character Card,,0,0,0,,Kojima Kanji (28)
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.64,0:03:49.57,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,What? Where's the proof? You can't hold us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.58,0:03:55.62,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Even if you refuse now, we'll come to your home later.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.59,0:03:58.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.72,0:04:00.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I get it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.01,0:04:01.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you then.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:04.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was listening to the horse race in the car.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.56,0:04:13.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The off-track waging office is in here, so if I won,\NI planned to go collect and then go shopping.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.66,0:04:16.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And, your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.25,0:04:19.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Kojima Kanji.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.13,0:04:21.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,K-Kojima!?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.46,0:04:24.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're the criminal{, aren't you?}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.47,0:04:29.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because you have the same last name as Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.26,0:04:30.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.18,0:04:32.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The number on your shirt is {solid evidence}the evidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.06,0:04:36.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hide from the Tokyo Spirits wears the number 11!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.35,0:04:40.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} is wearing a Tokyo Spirits shirt right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.27,0:04:47.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,{Are you }Stupid, the Spirits also have the quick Naoki on their team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.86,0:04:48.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's true, but still...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.45,0:04:55.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, we always called him "Genta" in front\Nof Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and never used "Kojima", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.20,0:05:03.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, since he wasn't aware his family name is\N"Kojima," that can't be why he pointed to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.34,0:05:04.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.75,0:05:08.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You're next. Why were you are?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.30,0:05:13.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I came to buy a bag for my girl, but they don't sell it here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.10,0:05:19.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was trying to hurry and get to the next store,\Nbut some guy was there fixing the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.06,0:05:21.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really, what a hassle.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.56,0:05:22.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What's your name?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.27,0:05:26.40,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's Genda.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.40,0:05:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Genta!?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:29.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.99,0:05:31.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,G-Genda!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.61,0:05:32.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genda Tatsuzou!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.53,0:05:35.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what you're implying, but I'm not "Genta".
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.58,0:05:38.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} probably misheard you as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.66,0:05:42.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And you're fat, just like Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.67,0:05:46.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's foolish, there are plenty of fat people.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.34,0:05:49.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The Professor and Inspector Megure, for example.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.72,0:05:55.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It'd be different if Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} knew these\Nthree were the only suspects, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.18,0:05:59.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I doubt think he'd leave such an oblivious hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:00.14,0:06:06.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, after Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pointed to Genta\Nand said, "Criminal", he also said "El".
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.73,0:06:10.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he knew his name, wouldn't he have just said "Genda"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.82,0:06:12.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess you're right...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.86,0:06:15.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And finally you. Why're you here?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.12,0:06:22.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just came to see the press event for the idol\NSakaguchi Ai on the sixth floor of this building.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.21,0:06:25.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,My name is Inagaki Hiromasa...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.71,0:06:27.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm just a fan.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.46,0:06:30.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hold on a second.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.13,0:06:34.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,On his driver's license, the kanji he uses for\N"Hiromasa" can also be used for "Taishou", right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.77,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.06,0:06:40.02,Signs,,0,0,0,,INAGAKI
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.35,0:06:39.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, if you took out the "Ina" kanji from your name...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.02,0:06:43.06,Signs,,0,0,0,,GAKIDAISHO
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.77,0:06:43.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Neighborhood Kids Leader"!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.69,0:06:45.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.95,0:06:48.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Weren't you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.24,0:06:51.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I just said Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} doesn't know the criminal's name.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.32,0:06:54.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But it's too convenient to be a coincidence!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.08,0:06:56.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A-And also, look at his hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.54,0:06:59.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It has a big "L" on it!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:01.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.13,0:07:06.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Official Sakaguchi Ai merchandise...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:07.09,0:07:09.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't think it's that "L" either.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.93,0:07:15.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he were referring to that hat, he would\Nhave said "love" instead of "El-".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.81,0:07:19.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, with him being German, maybe he couldn't read it...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.69,0:07:20.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Did you forget?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.02,0:07:25.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His previous wife was British, meaning he can speak English.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.98,0:07:28.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He would have definitely read L-O-V-E as "love".
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:32.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,KARAI\NSPICEY
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.28,0:07:32.07,Signs,,0,0,0,,TSURAI\NTRING
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.74,0:07:35.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't like Japanese where "karai" can be "tsurai" and\N"osatsu" can be "ofuda". (Spicy -> Tiring, Bill -> Label)
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:36.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,OSATSU\NBILL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.08,0:07:36.30,Signs,,0,0,0,,OFUDA\NLABEL
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.50,0:07:39.75,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.75,0:07:40.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's how it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.63,0:07:49.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Actually, there's a word in both German and English\Nthat's spelled the same, but has different meanings.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.53,0:07:53.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And? That relates to his message?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.63,0:07:54.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.76,0:07:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,His message was about another mischiveous boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.94,0:08:02.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey, Officer...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.06,0:08:03.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,When can we get outta here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.19,0:08:09.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was only here by chance, why should I have to stay here?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.95,0:08:13.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Not to mention, the press event will be over soon...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.57,0:08:17.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, but, we need to get your stories first.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.33,0:08:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I already told you!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.70,0:08:22.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I have nothing to do with this case!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.17,0:08:26.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I was in my car listening to the horse race.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.55,0:08:30.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,As I said earlier, I came here to get that bag.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.72,0:08:34.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Unfortunately, they don't even sell the damn bag here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.72,0:08:39.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I need to hurry off to the event and get a god seat.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.64,0:08:41.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't see anybody get attacked.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.48,0:08:42.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.02,0:08:51.74,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You three are saying that all three of you just happened to be here at the time, and yet none of you saw anything suspicious?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.24,0:08:53.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what we're saying.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.20,0:08:57.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I guess that means we're free to leave, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.87,0:08:59.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, what about that fat kid?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.66,0:09:05.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That guy pointed to him and said "criminal", didn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.92,0:09:09.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wouldn't that mean this boy did it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.38,0:09:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.76,0:09:14.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was down here kicking that ball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.76,0:09:20.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, isn't it more likely he accidentally kicked the ball and hit him?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:23.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta isn't the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.85,0:09:25.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ayumi...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.31,0:09:27.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer, are we done here?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:30.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, well...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.61,0:09:33.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} couldn't be the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.99,0:09:36.53,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The reason Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pointed at Genta...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.53,0:09:43.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Was to say that Genta had something in\Ncommon with the one who attacked him.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.21,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because just like Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, the culprit was...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.96,0:09:48.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mischevious{pesky} boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.46,0:09:52.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mischevious{pesky} boy?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.05,0:09:55.55,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you serious?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.89,0:09:58.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.72,0:10:01.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is a serious assault, not some mischief...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.18,0:10:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What I refer to is the very image.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.52,0:10:07.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see! That's it!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.02,0:10:09.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The criminal is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.98,0:10:11.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Inagaki Hiromasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.57,0:10:12.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's you, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.78,0:10:17.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Since you came for an idol's press event, you must have a camera!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.24,0:10:18.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thus, you're a camera kid!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.70,0:10:20.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A mischevious{pesky} boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.74,0:10:21.78,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No way...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.16,0:10:24.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A camera kid and a mischevious{pesky} boy are completely different.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.62,0:10:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But, they could be the same...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.87,0:10:27.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But then, but then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.08,0:10:30.58,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Doesn't that make this guy the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.59,0:10:31.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.00,0:10:34.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I bet he pulled a lot of pranks as a child!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.72,0:10:41.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The hell is going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.72,0:10:43.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How does that make me the criminal?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.10,0:10:51.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even so, Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}, how would Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}\Nknow how his childhood went?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.86,0:10:56.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That leaves us with this Genda guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.36,0:11:02.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But he looks more like a bad guy than someone into mischief...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.70,0:11:04.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He actually does seem bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.12,0:11:09.00,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please hold on a moment. That's not what I'm trying to say.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.00,0:11:11.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, could you please explain now?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.88,0:11:14.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It isn't Japanese, it's English...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.09,0:11:14.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.76,0:11:16.63,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.92,0:11:20.72,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The small fairies that appear in fantasy stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.55,0:11:22.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Fairies?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.68,0:11:25.03,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}Haibara...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.25,0:11:36.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The title "elf" can applied to a small kid...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.92,0:11:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But there's also another application which means a "mischevious{pesky} boy".
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.68,0:11:43.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.80,0:11:48.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That's why he said "El" after pointing to Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:50.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was trying to say "elf"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.93,0:11:53.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But how does that relate to Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.81,0:11:57.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,While it's true that Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} looks like the most mischevious{pesky},
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.05,0:12:01.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,a small fairy or elf should've been Ayumi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-chan{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:05.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's from when Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} kicked a soccer\Nball in here and hit Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}'s car.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.16,0:12:09.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After Genta did it, he called him...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.96,0:12:13.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A naughty boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.46,0:12:19.59,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was trying to say that the criminal was an elf like Genta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.96,0:12:22.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,A criminal elf?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.47,0:12:28.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see. The hint was to say the criminal was mischevious{pesky}, like an elf.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.85,0:12:33.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can see him saying that about Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.81,0:12:35.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.40,0:12:41.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I can't imagine any of these three as a small, prank loving fairy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.65,0:12:45.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you explain it, Agasa{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.28,0:12:53.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I failed to mention earlier that Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} is German\Nand can speak German, English, and Japanese.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.17,0:13:00.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So, when they asked who did it, the numbers\Nin his native language came to mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.55,0:13:01.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Numbers?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.96,0:13:02.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.80,0:13:05.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Um, let's see here...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.76,0:13:07.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Un, deux, trois...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.30,0:13:08.80,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, that's French.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.93,0:13:11.76,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,In German, one is "eins"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.06,0:13:14.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Two is "zwei"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.06,0:13:16.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Three is "drei"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:17.81,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Four is "vier"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.48,0:13:19.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Five is "funf"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.06,0:13:21.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Six is "sechs"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.77,0:13:23.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Seven is "sieben"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.57,0:13:24.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Eight is "acht"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.40,0:13:26.61,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Nine is "neun"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.28,0:13:28.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ten is "zehn"...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.36,0:13:30.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,And eleven is...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.70,0:13:32.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"Elf."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.03,0:13:33.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.12,0:13:37.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Kojima Kanji{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.62,0:13:42.42,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's the number on your back.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.88,0:13:54.47,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see, so Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} pointed at Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} and tried to say\N"eleven" and "elf", to give a German and English hint.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.81,0:13:58.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,With his knowledge of Germany and\NEngland, he went to Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.31,0:14:05.48,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, right, he hoped the Professor\Nwould be able to figure out its meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.48,0:14:10.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But if he knew Japanese, wouldn't it be easier\Nto have just said "eleven" in Japanese?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.16,0:14:17.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He probably did that on purpose, just in case the\Ncriminal were still nearby and saw us talking to him.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:21.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was afraid we would get attacked if we knew anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.50,0:14:23.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.09,0:14:27.96,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well then, Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}, would you please come with us?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.84,0:14:31.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You've gotta be joking, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.43,0:14:35.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I don't know what this elf thing is...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.72,0:14:39.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But why am I automatically the criminal for wearing the #11?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.44,0:14:43.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Besides, that German guy didn't even\Nget to completely say "elf", did he?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.94,0:14:44.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, Old man?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.52,0:14:50.99,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me this is all of your reasoning.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.40,0:14:54.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But his reasoning seems perfect...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.99,0:14:58.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You seemed confident back there, Old man.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.08,0:14:59.16,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.16,0:15:02.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm Japanese, not some stupid elf!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.62,0:15:03.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Please relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.29,0:15:09.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you think he's right, show me some proof.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.80,0:15:13.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You know, some proof that shows I'm the criminal.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.20,0:15:16.66,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, what's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.93,0:15:22.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,None of you saw me hit that foreigner and run away, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.02,0:15:29.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems like no one here can prove I did it...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.11,0:15:29.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.36,0:15:33.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, I guess we're done here.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.65,0:15:35.20,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Have a nice day.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.20,0:15:36.70,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait, Kojima{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.87,0:15:37.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.91,0:15:46.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw this man named Kojima hit Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} and run away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.00,0:15:48.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.54,0:15:49.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.84,0:15:51.71,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is that true, Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.30,0:15:58.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After I found Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} covered in\Nblood, I saw this man running away!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.01,0:16:00.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, brat!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.85,0:16:02.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys seen him too, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.10,0:16:04.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You guys seen him too, right!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.73,0:16:06.31,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.23,0:16:12.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You can't let him just say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.99,0:16:15.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Can you testify to that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.66,0:16:18.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, don't let him lie to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.57,0:16:20.41,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't you find this a bit strange!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.08,0:16:23.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If he saw me then, wouldn't he have said so from the start?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.29,0:16:30.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's just playing along with what that old bastard said!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.67,0:16:32.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He just made it up!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.17,0:16:36.01,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Regardless, we've known Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.34,0:16:37.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He's honest enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.30,0:16:38.43,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Are you insane!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.97,0:16:41.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How can you not see he's making this up!?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.22,0:16:42.18,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm not lying!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.56,0:16:46.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I even saw the number on your back!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.98,0:16:49.02,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Why you... If you don't shut up...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.86,0:16:50.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really did!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.69,0:16:51.73,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him! I saw him! I saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.90,0:16:55.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because I was the first one to find Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.24,0:16:58.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Conan{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:05.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you got that, Officer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.12,0:17:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I think you messed up, kid.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.37,0:17:11.33,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Remember? The first to find him was the fat one!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.54,0:17:13.46,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't you!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.60,0:17:22.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How'd you know...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.68,0:17:25.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That Genta was the first to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.44,0:17:29.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Takagi{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}, did we tell them that?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.90,0:17:32.27,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, no, we didn't...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.40,0:17:35.07,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.78,0:17:37.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,No, it's not like that...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.57,0:17:40.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh, that's right! I saw this kid by himself earlier.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.99,0:17:43.37,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was playing soccer by himself, earlier!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.24,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Really now?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.24,0:17:45.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.16,0:17:53.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I thought you were listening to horse racing\Nin your car and didn't hear Genta scream?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.55,0:17:57.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you didn't hear him scream...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.67,0:18:00.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How did you know he was first to find him?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.51,0:18:04.35,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I told you, I saw him!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.81,0:18:08.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I saw him kicking the ball by himself, so assumed...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.14,0:18:12.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even if I couldn't hear anything, I could've just looked out the window.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.11,0:18:14.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Right, Officer?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:14.86,0:18:16.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Even though that's true...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:17.24,0:18:20.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How could you know it was Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} just by that?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.66,0:18:23.57,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was just kicking the ball, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.57,0:18:26.12,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course I'd know, because at that time...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.12,0:18:26.87,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,At that time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.45,0:18:28.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.71,0:18:35.50,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's this, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.30,0:18:40.22,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,After you hit Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} with the steel pipe...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.30,0:18:46.30,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You saw this soccer ball come by and you knew, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.72,0:18:51.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You knew Genta, who was kicking the\Nball around, would come looking for it.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.81,0:18:53.65,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, no...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.36,0:18:57.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I really was listening to the horse race!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.53,0:18:58.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Then, why don't you tell us...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.74,0:19:02.45,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The name of the horse that won the main race today?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.45,0:19:08.08,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,If you were listening to the horse races, you'd have to know...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.08,0:19:12.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because we came back during the main race.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.50,0:19:14.67,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ah, see...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.75,0:19:18.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Of course, I don't expect you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.38,0:19:21.88,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Because after Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r}'s ball came by...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.84,0:19:25.64,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You tried to hurry out of the parking lot...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.93,0:19:33.60,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Only to realize that the broken gate was being\Nrepaired and Genda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r} was in front of you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.10,0:19:36.94,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,There's no way you could get out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.77,0:19:49.49,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next, you hid in your car to avoid the police and pretended\Nto have been listening to the horse race the entire time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.37,0:19:55.85,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Your heart was pounding and your mind was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.77,0:20:02.39,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.48,0:20:05.69,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It can't be.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.97,0:20:07.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.01,0:20:09.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It wasn't me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.56,0:20:09.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.35,0:20:18.06,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,You bastard, you're not getting away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.31,0:20:19.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do it, Genda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.44,0:20:21.15,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.32,0:20:23.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genda{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.20,0:20:25.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Don't do... it...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.78,0:20:32.83,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Well, at least now you'll know some of the pain you've caused.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:02.46,0:22:03.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.84,0:22:08.05,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,So the criminal did it just for the money?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.05,0:22:13.90,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, that's what Officer Takagi said when he called the\NProfessor earlier to thank him for solving the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:18.52,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,He was apparently on the run from loan sharks and got desperate.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.85,0:22:24.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It seems Japan's crimes are being more and more Americanized.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.94,0:22:28.28,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,But I'm so glad Genta{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-kun{\r} wasn't the criminal!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.03,0:22:32.32,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I had lost all reason to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.87,0:22:36.29,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,That was pretty cruel of that foreigner...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:36.83,0:22:39.62,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Pointing at a kid and saying "criminal".
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.12,0:22:41.54,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It really was, wasn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.46,0:22:44.38,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.59,0:22:47.84,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Genta could have really become a suspect.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.80,0:22:50.17,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I believed in them...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.68,0:22:54.10,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,These little detectives.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.10,0:22:54.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.39,0:22:58.93,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is everything OK with your head injury?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.93,0:23:00.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Yeah, mostly.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:00.14,0:23:01.14,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.65,0:23:04.11,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Is this that German?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.11,0:23:04.98,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It looks like it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.36,0:23:08.23,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.24,0:23:09.19,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.19,0:23:11.36,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Take this as a gift, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:13.16,0:23:14.91,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is cheesecake from that store!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.16,0:23:17.04,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,How nice!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.87,0:23:20.25,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I didn't get any the other day!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.71,0:23:22.79,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is my chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.83,0:23:25.13,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,I hope you enjoy it.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:25.13,0:23:27.34,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This is very thoughtful of you, Ludger{\rHonorifics - Dialogue}-san{\r}!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.34,0:23:28.09,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.55,0:23:34.26,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Hey, hey! Why did such a weak horse have to win!?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.51,0:23:36.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,This race should've been in the bag!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:37.01,0:23:37.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Uncle...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.06,0:23:40.68,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,It's not the strong one that wins...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.27,0:23:43.56,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The one that wins is strong!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.42,0:23:45.82,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.82,0:23:54.12,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The criminal may be in this building still.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:57.42,0:23:59.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}I have to go down these stairs.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:59.72,0:24:02.36,Thoughts,,0,0,0,,{\be10}The other stairs are blocked.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:02.72,0:24:04.95,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,The target is probably...
Dialogue: 0,0:24:12.32,0:24:17.92,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan, "Real 30 Minutes"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.64,0:24:20.44,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,Next Conan's Hint:
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.44,0:24:22.97,Dialogue,,0,0,0,,"A Live TV Show"
Dialogue: 0,0:24:23.84,0:24:25.24,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Next episode is a live!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:25.24,0:24:26.44,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,It's the first attempt in Japanese Anime history, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:24:26.44,0:24:27.74,Dialogue Top,,0,0,0,,Just kidding.
